web.feedback.help_us_improve.translation: Hjælp os med at forbedre os

web.feedback.thanks_for_helping_onetime_.en: Thanks for helping Onetime Secret improve. It means a lot.
web.feedback.thanks_for_helping_onetime_.translation: Tak, fordi du hjalp Onetime Secret med at blive bedre. Det betyder meget.

web.feedback.weve_built_this_tool_to_hel.en: We've built this tool to help you share sensitive info securely, and your real-world experiences are crucial for focusing our efforts. It helps us figure out what to work on next and how to make the service better for everyone.
web.feedback.weve_built_this_tool_to_hel.translation: Vi har bygget dette værktøj for at hjælpe dig med at dele følsomme oplysninger sikkert, og dine erfaringer fra den virkelige verden er afgørende for at fokusere vores indsats. Det hjælper os med at finde ud af, hvad vi skal arbejde videre med, og hvordan vi kan gøre tjenesten bedre for alle.

web.feedback.hey_there_thanks_for_stoppi.en: Hey there, thanks for stopping by our feedback page. Your input isn't just welcome - it's crucial.
web.feedback.hey_there_thanks_for_stoppi.translation: Hejsa, tak fordi du kiggede forbi vores feedback-side. Dit input er ikke bare velkomment - det er afgørende.

web.feedback.a_note_from_delano_founder_.en: A note from Delano, founder of Onetime Secret
web.feedback.a_note_from_delano_founder_.translation: En note fra Delano, grundlægger af Onetime Secret
